             depos'd. That he living two Doors from Mr.Vevers, saw him pass by his Door between 6 and 7 on Easter Monday Morning, having on a white Fustian Frock, and a leather Apron.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17270412-44-person278">
