             depos'd. That he was at Mr.Vevers's House before 6, when Mr. Vevers was in Bed, and getting up, gave him the Key of his Work, which was a Building in Holloway Lane Shoreditch; and that about 6, or something after, this Deponent went with Mr. Vevers to a Timber Merchant's in White-Lion Yard near Shoreditch, where this Deponent left him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17270412-44-person279">
                  Tho.
                   Grange
               <interp inst="t17270412-44-person279" type="surname" value="Grange"></interp>
