                  </persName>
             depos'd, That the Prosecutor's Master told him that he Robert Gun made it a common Practice to embezzle his Master's Money. These things, and the positive Evidence Mr. Vevers had in his behalf, being judiciously examin'd into by the Court, and consider'd by the Jury he was <rs id="t17270412-44-verdict219" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17270412-44-verdict219" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs>; and a Copy of his Indictment granted him.</p>
